observations.recommendation:
We recommend that Management direct the Municipal Planning and Development Office to strictly comply with the provision of COA Circular No. 2013-004 on the requirement to submit the list of all on- going government projects/programs/activities and those that are to be implemented during the year containing the following information:
a. The project name;
b. Implementing unit, office or division if it is not the agency as a whole;
c. Brief description of the PPA;
d. Contractor or supplier, if any;
e. Mode of procurement;
f. Funding source;
g. Cost or approved budget;
h. Project duration including start and completion dates; and
i. Location

